Installation Instructions:

1.  Open truevirtual.cgi and enter the title of your own page as well as the url.
2.  Modify the database file using the template included.
3.  Upload the files to the server.   BE SURE TO UPLOAD IN ASCII MODE!!
4.  Chmod truevirtual.cgi 755 and chmod database 666.
5.  Rename your current index.html file something like home.html (or whatever you decided in step one)
6.  Create a new index.shtml file containing the following line only:
	<!--#exec cgi="/cgi-bin/truevirtual/truevirtual.cgi"-->

Special Notes:
• This script requires server side includes and will not work otherwise.

